description: Retrieves the device position history from a tracker resource within a specified range of time.

parameters.name: TrackerName
parameters.description: The tracker resource receiving the request for the device position history.

parameters.name: DeviceId
parameters.description: The device whose position history you want to retrieve.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The pagination token specifying which page of results to return in the response. If no token is provided, the default page is the first page. Default value: null.

parameters.name: StartTimeInclusive
parameters.description: Specify the start time for the position history in ISO 8601 format: YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss.sssZ. By default, the value will be 24 hours prior to the time that the request is made. Requirement: The time specified for StartTimeInclusive must be before EndTimeExclusive.

parameters.name: EndTimeExclusive
parameters.description: Specify the end time for the position history in ISO 8601 format: YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss.sssZ. By default, the value will be the time that the request is made. Requirement: The time specified for EndTimeExclusive must be after the time for StartTimeInclusive.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: An optional limit for the number of device positions returned in a single call. Default value: 100

nested_items.name: DevicePositions
nested_items.description: Contains the position history details for the requested device.

nested_items.name: DeviceId
nested_items.description: The device whose position you retrieved.

nested_items.name: SampleTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp at which the device's position was determined. Uses ISO 8601 format: YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss.sssZ.

nested_items.name: ReceivedTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp for when the tracker resource received the device position in ISO 8601 format: YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss.sssZ.

nested_items.name: Horizontal
nested_items.description: Estimated maximum distance, in meters, between the measured position and the true position of a device, along the Earth's surface.

nested_items.name: PositionProperties
nested_items.description: The properties associated with the position.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A pagination token indicating there are additional pages available. You can use the token in a following request to fetch the next set of results.
